    "notes": [
      {
        "category": "summary",
        "text": "An update is available for flatpak.\nThis update affects Rocky Linux 9.\nA Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE list",
        "title": "Topic"
      },
      {
        "category": "description",
        "text": "Flatpak is a system for building, distributing, and running sandboxed desktop applications on Linux.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* flatpak: sandbox escape via RequestBackground portal (CVE-2024-32462)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n\nThis advisory is provided by Ctrl IQ, Inc for Rocky Linux systems. For more information about CIQ security practices, visit https://ciq.com/security.",
        "title": "Description"
      }
    ],
